ActFisheries Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Marine Mammal Regulations (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations Amending the MARINE MAMMAL REGULATIONS in order to correct an error with respect to the geographic area described in section 7.2(2)(e) of the Regulations. This section currently creates an exception for helicopters being used in seal pup observation in the St. Lawrence Estuary.
